4 Gerschizhevsky: a Slavist’s name gets mixed here with that of Chizhevki, another Slavist.

5 Je ne peux etc.: I can do nothing, but nothing.

6 Buchstaben: Germ., letters of the alphabet.

7 c’est tout simple: it’s quite simple.

